OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776604038
OL,3,CBoy dies after crash involving bus and
OL,4,Ccar in Derby
OL,6,FAn 11-year-old boy has died after a
OL,7,Fcrash involving a bus and a car in
OL,8,FDerby.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FNottingham Road, in Chaddesden, just
OL,12,Fbefore 7pm on Friday, April 17.
OL,14,FPolice said an 11-year-old boy, who
OL,15,Fwas cycling at the time, suffered
OL,16,Fserious injuries and died in hospital.
OL,18,FA statement from the force reads: "We
OL,19,Fare appealing for witnesses and
OL,20,Fdashcam footage after a fatal
OL,21,Fcollision in Derby.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
