OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776604038
OL,3,CBoy dies after crash involving bus and
OL,4,Ccar in Derby
OL,6,F"The collision, which involved a bus,
OL,7,Fa car and a cyclist, occurred in
OL,8,FNottingham Road just before 6.45pm on
OL,9,FFriday 17 April.
OL,11,F"His family are aware and are being
OL,12,Fsupported by specialist officers. Our
OL,13,Fthoughts are with them at this time."
OL,15,FThe force said no arrests have been
OL,16,Fmade.
OL,18,FAnyone with information can contact
OL,19,Fpolice on 101, quoting the reference
OL,20,F26000220550.
